<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><author>Upa Kapzinga</author>
<hymn_number>40</hymn_number>
<title>Kalvari Tang Khu</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Galin dawn leu hing,
 Kalvari tang A thihna mun khu;
 Khawvel Hukdampa, I Lalpau Isu,
 Lungkham leh thavaih na'n Amah abawm,

[V2]
 A chiehna ding chu aw ka thil ngam puoi
 Juda mipi leh melmate lakah;
 Ka gitloh ziekin, aw ka Lal Isu,

[V3]
 2. Aw, Na hehpihna,
 Lungngaih kinawkin Kalvari ah,
 Keihaw nei tantai vakmang gimtheite
 Ka gitloh thienna, aw na thisan lul.

[V4]
 3. Zie Khawvel a hin,
 Vakvai gimtheite nei hung hawl tai;
 Na angsung mun muong chu ka hungtun ma'n,
 Ka hun hawl zel hi, Aw ka Hukdampa.</lyrics>
</song>